#OS 

products2 <- products %>% 
  mutate( = as.yearmon(as.character(), "%Y%m")) %>%
  rename(date = "") %>%
  filter(OS != "") %>%
  group_by(date, OS) %>%
  summarise(mean = mean())

products_line <- products2 %>% 
  data_grid(date, OS) %>%
  gather_predictions(lm(mean ~ date * OS, data = products2))

products2 %>%
  ggplot(aes(date, mean, colour = OS)) +
  geom_line(lwd = 2) +
  geom_line(data = products_line, aes(y = pred),lwd = 1) +
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=12),
        axis.title=element_text(size=14,face="bold")) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.title = element_text(size = 15, face = "bold")) +
  theme(legend.text = element_text(size = 12))

# 

products %>%
  filter(OS == "") %>%
  group_by(, OS) %>%
  summarise(mean = mean()) %>%
  arrange(desc(mean)) %>%
  head(10) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = reorder(, -mean), y = mean)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", position = "dodge", width=.5, fill = "#619CFF") + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle=65, vjust=0.6,)) + 
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=12),
        axis.title=element_text(size=14,face="bold")) +
  theme_bw()
